Glory Seeker: Cleave the Enemy

Allow a scout to lead you into the Ettenmoors

'[placeholder], I ask you to champion our cause in the Ettenmoors. I shall afford you a measure of strength should you endeavour to assail and bring low every enemy out of Angmar you discover.

'Seek glory in this battle. Gain strength with your victories and reap the reward should you succeed where others may fail.

'But, know this, the enemy will know your name. They will see through your wiliest guise and come for you on the battlefield.

'Will you dare to be glorious?'

<rgb=#FF0000>Accepting this quest will teleport you to the forward Elf Camp in the Ettenmoors and expose your position on the Ettenmoors and mini-map.</rgb>
